    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chorizo has been cooking for 3-4 min add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>drained</strong> <strong>cannellini beans</strong>,<strong> dried oregano</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> with 25ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[40ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[50ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min or until the garlic has softened and the water has evaporated – these are your <strong>chorizo beans</strong></p>",
